column3: Could you combine this with #5602 ? Rather than opening multiple pull requests just to fix typos.\n
BTW, for things like this if you add [skip ci] or [ci skip] in the commit message, it'll save Travis the trouble of going and building and testing the software again for something like this.\n
This is part of @theuni's trivial tree (https://github.com/theuni/bitcoin-trivial/commits/trivial-rebase) and will be merged via that route, so closing this pull.\n
